{"version":1,"source":"indexeddb-geo2025-snapshot","modified":1782096381181,"work":{"id":241543,"cn":"另一位魔女／另一段生命","title":"もうひとりの魔女","city":"神奈川县","color":"#0fb5d7","cover":"/images/bangumi/241543.jpg","fade":7.3,"cat":"小说","geo":[35.314909,139.548298],"zoom":14,"points":[{"id":"jey57n63f","geo":[35.319374,139.5513],"priority":15,"name":"小町通り","isFolder":false,"mid":"1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0","uid":1057,"s":"","mark":"以红色鸟居为大门，左右两侧被诸多商家填满的这条路上，观光客比当地人还多。——《另一位魔女》 藤泽②","density":15,"origin":"@AmaiAya","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0&ll=35.319374%2C139.5513"},{"id":"jey57n5mu","geo":[35.319462,139.5514],"priority":31,"name":"イワタコーヒー店","isFolder":false,"mid":"1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0","uid":1057,"s":"","mark":"她就这样带我进去。店内装潢彷佛配合来访古都的观光客，与其说时尚，不如说统一采用低调的配色。照明略显昏暗，沙发是咖啡色的。带点温暖的颜色，让并不具体的过往稍稍浮现出来。——《另一段生命》 七里／七里的手指向一栋著名的米色建筑物，窗户虽然擦得晶亮，但正面的橱窗有些脏污。摆设在橱窗里的料理模型已经有些斑驳，显露年代感。外头的观叶植物曾几何时开出了红色花朵。——《另一位魔女》 藤泽②","density":15,"origin":"@AmaiAya","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0&ll=35.319462%2C139.5514"},{"id":"jey57n5yw","geo":[35.309269,139.542222],"priority":33,"name":"由比ガ浜海水浴場","isFolder":false,"mid":"1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0","uid":1057,"s":"","mark":"《另一位魔女》封面","density":1508,"origin":"@AmaiAya","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0&ll=35.309269%2C139.542222"},{"id":"jey57n6e6","geo":[35.299099,139.480927],"priority":999,"name":"江の島","isFolder":false,"mid":"1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0","uid":1057,"s":"","mark":"「你记得江之岛吗？」 藤泽缓缓看向道路后方。「在那一头。」她指了指海的方向。我花了一点时间才明白她是在说那个江之岛。——《另一段生命》 和田冢","density":6897,"origin":"@AmaiAya","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1qHDo5HWlMAXbM6I9riaUQgnneHMJqQ0&ll=35.299099%2C139.480927"}],"tags":["入间人间"],"priority":999,"icon":null,"modified":1723991941120,"pointsLength":4,"imagesLength":0},"points":[{"id":"jey57n63f","geo":[35.319374,139.5513],"priority